elements.name: accountingClassCode1
elements.description: CBP accounting classification code representing a specific fee type previously reported at the Entry Summary Header Fee (34-Record) or Line User Fee (62-Record) level.

elements.name: totalFeeAmount1
elements.description: Total estimated fee amount that corresponds to Accounting Class Code (1) in U.S. dollars and cents. Two decimal places are implied.
